Enum APIOutputMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<APIOutputMode>
      • com.digi.xbee.api.models.APIOutputMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<APIOutputMode>

    public enum APIOutputMode
extends Enum<APIOutputMode>
    Enumerates the different API output modes. The API output mode establishes the way data will be output through the serial interface of an XBee device.
